{"tid":1289174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搵到 政總餐廳 個廢老李生","createTime":"2019-07-06T03:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T15:07:07.000Z","uid":274646,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5be474f7b91a542d4f5392e10a4d1f4de96966ad","tid":1289174,"uid":274646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:45:14.000Z","msg":"佢叫李炳輝，原來佢專門經營政府飯堂，另一間是金鐘高等法院裡的食堂。<br />\n<br />\n佢之前亦做過     &quot;警察學堂&quot;    的飯堂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n靠政府判野比佢做，咁大利益你話到時上法庭佢會幫邊個，你話如果佢幫左政府後政府會唔會判多d比佢做？<br />\n<br />\n間公司叫嘉嘉得，出面仲有好多間餐廳叫gaga 餐廳<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=gaga%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3+%E5%98%89%E5%98%89%E5%BE%97&amp;tbm=isch&amp;ved=2ahUKEwihw7flj57jAhVmx4sBHcN5Ba8Q2-cCegQIABAB&amp;oq=gaga%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3+%E5%98%89%E5%98%89%E5%BE%97&amp;gs_l=mobile-gws-wiz-img.12...24883.31446..31998...4.0..0.102.839.5j4......0....1.MdG2AGUNwu8&amp;ei=pnAfXaHYM-aOr7wPw_OV-Ao&amp;prmd=minv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dgaga%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3%2B%25E5%2598%2589%25E5%2598%2589%25E5%25BE%2597%26tbm%3Disch%26ved%3D2ahUKEwihw7flj57jAhVmx4sBHcN5Ba8Q2-cCegQIABAB%26oq%3Dgaga%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3%2B%25E5%2598%2589%25E5%2598%2589%25E5%25BE%2597%26gs_l%3Dmobile-gws-wiz-img.12...24883.31446..31998...4.0..0.102.839.5j4......0....1.MdG2AGUNwu8%26ei%3DpnAfXaHYM-aOr7wPw_OV-Ao%26prmd%3Dminv&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=31222a95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/search?q=gaga%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3+%E5%98%89%E5%98%89%E5%BE%97&amp;tbm=isch&amp;ved=2ahUKEwihw7flj57jAhVmx4sBHcN5Ba8Q2-cCegQIABAB&amp;oq=gaga%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3+%E5%98%89%E5%98%89%E5%BE%97&amp;gs_l=mobile-gws-wiz-img.12...24883.31446..31998...4.0..0.102.839.5j4......0....1.MdG2AGUNwu8&amp;ei=pnAfXaHYM-aOr7wPw_OV-Ao&amp;prmd=minv</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明報內容：<br />\n示威者衝入立法會後，裏內的餐廳亦不倖免，其所屬的嘉嘉得飲食有限公司董事李先生說：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190703/s00001/1562091763208/%E3%80%8C%E5%81%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%AA%E7%9B%A1%E3%80%8D-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%82%94%E6%B2%92%E9%98%BB%E5%90%8C%E4%BC%B4%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190703%2Fs00001%2F1562091763208%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%259B%25A1%25E3%2580%258D-%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2582%2594%25E6%25B2%2592%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=e7853df1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190703%2Fs00001%2F1562091763208%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%259B%25A1%25E3%2580%258D-%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2582%2594%25E6%25B2%2592%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E&h=4165d7fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190703/s00001/1562091763208/%E3%80%8C%E5%81%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%AA%E7%9B%A1%E3%80%8D-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%82%94%E6%B2%92%E9%98%BB%E5%90%8C%E4%BC%B4%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E</a>[/quote]"},{"pid":"7b4a52827ec624d6e70687d55f6c8675bcdddce8","tid":1289174,"uid":108337,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:49:17.000Z","msg":"消防設備有冇問題<br />\n衛生有冇問題"},{"pid":"ae989e030a740633fd7de3ce770961496cbc3fb5","tid":1289174,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:52:28.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"baa4f1dc476c659d92c495b4745eb35f4eef3c5e","tid":1289174,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:53:18.000Z","msg":"我無野請"},{"pid":"530d6ad92fce116d96a09be6caf01114cdbbd1a1","tid":1289174,"uid":274646,"like":9,